@node Main "IxTiles - Documentation"

                              'IxTiles' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'IxTiles' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} in which you have to remove all
coloured tiles on a 7 by 7 spaces board. Tiles in each space are
placed one above another, up to 4 in height. Each time you click
on one tile, and there are tiles of the same colour next to it,
these tiles will be removed from the board, this will reveal tiles
that are located under, if there are any. You get points according
to the number of removed tiles.

  Have fun!

