@node play "The game: Installation/Playing"

                             Installation

  The installation is very simple, just place 'IxTiles' where you
want on your hard drive, floppy disk, Ram Disk, etc. No other files
or Libraries are needed. However, your Workbench must have at least
8 colours.

                             How to play?

  The gameplay is very simple, click on any coloured tile on the
game board. If there are tiles of the same colour next to it,
either at right, left, up or down, these tiles will be removed and
you will get points according to number of removed tiles, as shown
on the following table:

  2 tiles = 1 point
  3 tiles = 4 points
  4 tiles = 16 points
  5 tiles = 64 points

  As tiles are removed, they will reveal tiles that are located
under, if there are any. You cannot see the colour of tiles that
are located under until the uppermost tile has been removed.

  When all tiles have been removed from the board, IxTiles will
display a new board to play with and the game will continue. The
game ends when there are no tiles of the same colour next to each
other...

  Have fun!

  To quit the game, click on the game window's close button or
press the 'Esc' key.

@endnode

